MultiLegSwitchId, Tradeletternummer en-versie overnemen voor herberekening van Multileg switch percentages

switchorders in een tradeletter gegroepeerd per verkoop-fonds: de orders voor dit fonds krijgen allemaal
hetzelfde TLO_SIWTCH_MULTILEG_ID.

SQL_STMT_U.val: update trade_letter_order o set o.tlo_switch_multileg_perc = 100 * o.tlo_instrument1_quantity / (select sum(os.tlo_instrument1_quantity) from trade_letter_order os where os.tlo_switch_multileg_id = ~1 and os.tlo_no = ~2 and os.tlo_version = ~3) where o.tlo_switch_multileg_id = ~1 and o.tlo_no = ~2 and o.tlo_version = ~3

SQL_STMT_U.val: select sum(o.tlo_switch_multileg_perc) from trade_letter_order o where o.tlo_switch_multileg_id = ~1 and o.tlo_no = ~2 and o.tlo_version = ~3

select o.tlo_id from trade_letter_order o where o.tlo_switch_multileg_id = ~1 and o.tlo_no = ~2 and o.tlo_version = ~3 and o.tlo_switch_multileg_perc = (select max(t.tlo_switch_multileg_perc) from trade_letter_order t where t.tlo_switch_multileg_id = o.tlo_switch_multileg_id) and rownum <= 1
